    {
      "modelVersion": "gemini-2.5-flash",
      "content": {
        "parts": [
          {
            "text": "Hello! I'm a multilingual content agent. I can help you with:\n\n**Translation:**\n*   Detecting the language of a text string.\n*   Detecting text on an image.\n*   Translating text from one language to another (I can also detect the source language if you don't specify it).\n*   Translating text found in image files.\n\n**Transcription:**\n*   Transcribing audio from video files (mp4, mov).\n*   Transcribing audio files using different models (`chirp`, `chirp_2`, `chirp_telephony`).\n*   Cleaning up or correcting transcripts.\n*   Generating a synopsis from transcripts.\n\n**Saving Results:**\n*   Saving text outputs to Google Cloud Storage (GCS) in `txt`, `vtt`, or `pdf` formats.\n\nIf you want to attach a file locally, please ensure it does not exceed 32MB. How can I assist you today?",
